CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

January 8, 2014

[Cite as 01/08/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-16.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1913. Calvary SPV I, L.L.C. v. Gabelman.

Licking App. No. 13-CA-15, 2013-Ohio-4663. This cause is pending before the court as a jurisdictional appeal.

Upon consideration of appellants’ motion to strike and replace the pleading of Connie M. Gabelman and Mark J. Gabelman, it is ordered by the court that the motion is granted. The clerk’s office shall replace the December 5, 2013 memorandum in support of jurisdiction with the version attached to the motion to strike.
